title: Starts of the Week + Week 16 Breakdown, Touchdowns or Revolt! - Fantasy Football Podcast for 12/23
description:
Week 16 is here and The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Week 16 matchup previews and Starts of the Week! Plus, injury updates, a new edition of “Never Not Working,” and the Boom Boom Kicker story continues! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for December 23rd, 2021.
  
 (05:30) - Never Not Working
 (13:15) - NFL News
 (22:50) - Fantasy Forecast 
 (23:30) - Browns at Packers
 (28:05) - Colts at Cardinals
 (34:30) - Lions at Falcons
 (38:20) - Ravens at Bengals
 (43:55) - Rams at Vikings
 (46:45) - Bills at Patriots
 (52:40) - Jaguars at Jets
 (55:50) - Giants at Eagles 
 (59:00) - Starts of the Week
 (01:04:50) - Boom Boom Kicker of the Week
